data.description: Discover comfort and style in this charming Fairburn residence with 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms! This family-friendly gem features 2 stories, a spacious living area, a modern kitchen, and a two-car garage. Enjoy easy access to Hartsfield-Jackson International Airport, schools, restaurants, downtown, and more! Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this charming home yours!
